TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$k = random(1,5,1);$k4=4*$k;
$h = random(1,5,1);$h4=4*$h;
$r = random(1,1.4*sqrt($k**2+$h**2),1);
$c = 2*($k**2+$h**2-$r**2);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
\( 2 x^2+2 y^2+$h4 x+$k4 y +$c=0 \) is the equation of a circle with center \( (h,k) \) and radius \( r \) for:$BR
$BR
\( h= \)\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = -$h;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and$BR
\( k= \) \{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = -$k;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and$BR
\( r= \) \{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $r;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
